Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you do on your days off?\N- I heard your radio show yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, how about \Nsome tea later today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin, you should go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long will this scene continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin is a current pop idol after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this happening\Nis very understandable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a clue,\Nbut it's better if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Sound You Heard Sometime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, the one for Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the one for Yuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Group torture? How terrible....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's understandable...\Nwhen she does stuff like that impulsively...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have something to complain about?\NYou were just watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the helper is going to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got tortured by a mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?\NShouldn't you go to a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go pummel them all in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't going. That's too much of a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ability... is floating on air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"A flying humanoid is \Nfound in Japan as well"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it saying that this black shadow\Nis that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, it's only a scoop\Non an occult magazine like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we leave this alone,\Nthis will turn into a huge deal. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is in the middle of the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just speculation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I think that's where this person\Nis practicing how to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, if we keep staking out at this location,\Nthat person should appear at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep staking out?\NFor how long are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course until this person shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,$#@%!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make Yusarin say something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to procure food for all of us,\Nlet's go to the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... can you go back to Yusa, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's something I'll decide!\NWhy do I have to follow your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it ends up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'll burn you right here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this team all right..?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See here, I'll burn you now! See here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it all corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you think barbeque,\Nyou gotta have roasted corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Barbeque? If you do something like that,\Nyou'd get found out from the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This person may decide\Nto approach us instead, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is such a thing possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What else? Steak meat, spare ribs, wieners...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now you're thinking only about meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But meat is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shishito peppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The spice gives a nice accent to flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to eat them all,\Nthen that's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those two get along very well.\NCan they be dating each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.55,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy more hams and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been long since they first met,\Nso I don't think it's gone that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.68,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. We should get pumpkins instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But well, they are a couple\Nthat is pleasant to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.35,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think they're well \Nsuited for each other, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All alone with Yusarin! I'm glad I'm alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Boys,\Ngrab the tent and the barbeque grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kurobane and I will grab the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tent? So we're going to spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that we're going to keep staking out\Nuntil the ability wielder shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I didn't bring any change of clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't die even if you \Ndon't change clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should set \Nup the tent before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's dangerous over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What hole is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the remnants of a well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew about it,\Nyou could have told me about it earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you fell,\Nthat would have been funny in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make jokes that involve\Nlife-or-death situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's set it up a bit further that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, I'll take responsibility\Nand plug up that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but there's a student council camp\Nso I don't think I can go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This suddenly? You can't come home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is useful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use me as a lighter!\NHow senseless are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you thinking?\NThis makes us stand out way too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roasted corn is so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll yield this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, have some roasted corn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? Leave it to me \Nif it's about roasted corn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After this... Meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat vegetables, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spare ribs are so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The wieners are so juicy\Nwhen you crunch into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat just meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sandwich some vegetables in the middle\Nwhen you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This meat is so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sauce is good too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm the only \None eating vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You all eat only meat? \NYou're all like Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's a very finicky eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She... well, your big sister...\Nwhat kind of a person was she for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Big Sister and I\Nhave basically polar opposite personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And she was such a tomboy that no boy\Nin the neighborhood could win against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, she was a very kind big sister.\NAnd I loved her the way she was, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always tagged along behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess I've been talking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to Big Sister,\NI just get so engrossed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I kind of understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many enemies!\NYusarin is in a crisis, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! Leave it all to me—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-The point where I can show off..!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys are completely forgetting\Nthe reason why we're here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that music you're \Nalways listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This? It's a band called ZHIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the band that my big brother loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I listen to that for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've felt this before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:10:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow... I get a strange feeling\Nthat I'm standing all alone in a vast open space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand it, don't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The music ZHIEND creates\Nis very vast and downright lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's because the vocalist\Nwho also composes the songs is blind in both eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The imagery is that of scenery\Nextending as far as you can go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'm merely recording \Nthis poor fiend of cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But my dream is to film a ZHIEND music video.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen this expression \Non her face before....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would be okay with a documentary\Nfollowing ZHIEND's activity, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Don't film poor old me.\NPlease go ahead and film them..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll never film you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give that to you, including the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that would make me feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have quite a bit saved up\Nthanks to jobs concerning abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll buy a new one. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... then, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do night watch in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First off, you guys sleep for four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you wake up,\Ntake our spots and watch till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, it's our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, time to switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's that time already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This again... who was that person...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A rainbow trout! I fished a rainbow trout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'll fish up one bigger than that!\NTrout, trout, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbow trouts are tasty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin, this one is roasted in a good way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Yusarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I guess I'll yield it to Yusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this are nice \Nevery so often, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can it be that she just wants to play..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are we spending the \Nnight here again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I wanted to take a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I have one all \Nready. Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This is..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a towel and some soap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You got all this ready\Non the assumption that I'll do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep proper watch of the boys for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said there was a bath all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boys can go wipe themselves \Ndown at the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I can't bathe in the water\Nthat Yusarin has bathed in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the type\Nthat looks thinner when clothed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my ability, \NI had to train my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much armor\NI wore under my uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had to build a body\Nthat wouldn't get too injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You went that far\Njust to properly use your ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But this may not be merely\Nother people's business, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, there may \Nbe a challenge for you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is beyond all your expectations.\NThat's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With an ability that lets me take over someone\Nfor only 5 seconds, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's for you to—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? How you put it gets me curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With that attractive a face,\Nyou might have issues dealing with women...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want to say that\Nbecause I'm annoyed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just dumped by a intelligent\Nand beautiful girl thanks to this ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a wise choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love and romance should be built up\Nafter we are freed of these abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just exactly how old do we need to be\Nfor them to be gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should be gone\Nby the time we graduate from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two more years, huh... that's a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. For us, it is a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case... this is too cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This warms me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll sleep\Nusing the same rotation as yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is Monday, right?\NAre we going to head straight to school from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been telling you from the beginning\Nthat we're staking out until the person shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just too impossible...\Nit's as if we're living here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, ditching class\Nwill not affect our school reports at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'd really like to go home.\NI have a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll promise to be back in the morning,\Nso let me go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. If I allow that for you,\Neveryone else will say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I think it will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe everything\Nwill be squared out by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Corn again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone really showed up! Is it this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we all ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We each have our own reasons,\Nbut we just hit it off really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another obvious lie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean you're going\Nto continue staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We're planning on staying here forever.\NBecause people won't find us out if we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I found you out.\NI'm sure your parents are worried as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you call the police,\Nyou'll be detained as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is private property.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Private property - Keep out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A scoop article of you practicing flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flight..?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In mountains that people can normally enter,\Nyou can easily catch the eye of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place is close, and for you,\Na convenient mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we camped out,\Nand don't seem to show any signs of leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got restless,\Nand showed yourself before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that you could shoo us away,\Nthen practice your flying once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fly. You must be insane.\NI'll call the police for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're pretty insane yourself\Nfor coming all the way out here all alone, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pick some chestnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any chestnuts\Nthis time of the year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I already recorded evidence\Nthat you were here at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me. I'll erase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She used the well as a pitfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you fall into a hole\Nthat you don't know the bottom of,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'd use your ability and fly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I had shoved some hay\Nat the bottom for cushioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to you,\NI have an amazing footage for a scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A trap that she didn't even tell us about!\NShe is just like the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, take over his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat him using my teleport\Nwhile you're taking him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it because it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice but to do it..!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What height!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to control it for \Nnow! Stop! Stop! Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You took such a reckless risk there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should have just taken over him immediately\Ninstead of complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a bruise or a broken bone.\NThat's good enough for an end result.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My camcorder is fine, too.\NIt's a good thing you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all have special abilities as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, these abilities are like diseases\Nthat only show up during adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will disappear in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, if someone finds out about your ability,\Nyou become a guinea pig for scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what if your ability disappeared\Nwhile you are flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll fall to your death, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something to risk your life doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that this power was something granted\Njust to me... but there were others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to someday freely \Nfly through the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I even had a dream of becoming\NSkyhigh Saito the Hollywood star...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a corny name!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that feeling, but for yourself as well,\Nplease don't use that ability from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That ended peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that took so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really. That's totally how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think the student council\Nwas something this busy... I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, you're very competent.\NAre you being pulled all over the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that extravagant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to my big brother who is doing his best\Nwith student council activities, I have a feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chanpon noodles with lots of vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not red... This is... doable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! So delicious it makes me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to use the pizza sauce\Nas a secret ingredient, but I only have a tiny bit left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can make food this delicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can leave the pizza sauce out\Nof all the other food, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Otosaka pizza sauce is a secret recipe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that needs to be handed down\Nto the very last generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I was about to \Ngo to the supermarket,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the security guard stopped me for some reason,\Nand I couldn't buy the ingredients...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nice security! This is the first incident\Nthat makes me feel happy about moving here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is delicious on its own,\Nso you don't need any secret ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, that saves me a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! In the end,\NI succeeded in sealing away that pizza sauce!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really aren't feeling well after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had so many stories I wanted you to hear\Nwhile you were gone, Big Brother Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu was suddenly asked out\Nby one of the boy classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put on an air...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I politely declined the offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, that could have been a pivotal moment\Nthat changes your entire life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Yu, you wanted Ayu\Nto have a boyfriend or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really does have to be someone better\Nthan Big Brother Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like that doesn't \Ncome by all that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're feverish... how's your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I can finish eating all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,37.8 degrees...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You totally have caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After your body warms up by taking a bath,\Nyou need to crawl into your futon immediately. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fall asleep like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Sleep tight. Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well... if she stays put, \Nit should be all right.{\i0}
